Oh my gosh!!
Never heard any song like this before!! It just stole my mind and my heart too. Even though I couldn't understand anything but loved the song and their voices and the musics as well.

The language has such cute and satisfying words in it I'm willing to learn poshto language.Plz help me.
Love you pakistan, love you Afghanistan.
Lots of love from *India* 😊❤✌
